trans-unit.source: DHIS2 is more than just a piece of software. As you’ve learned, it is a community effort that wouldn’t be possible without the people who research, develop, implement, localize and use the platform. This community effort is facilitated by a range of initiatives, programs, platforms and tools that make up the DHIS2 ecosystem.
In this video, you’ll discover the different parts of the ecosystem, and how you can get involved. Click the play button below to get started.
